GLFW Binding for Red Language (http://www.red-lang.org/)F. Jouen (francois.jouen@ephe.sorbonne.fr)This binding has been extensively tested with Mac OSX 10.9.1 and works fine under OSX. Please adapt path to libraries according your main OS.glfw.reds is the binding for Redopgl.reds is a very quick done binding to OpenGL to be used with Red since GLFW requires OpenGL.This was done mainly for testing purpose and should be improved ASAP.You can also use use Kaj de Vos's wrapping for opengl (http://red.esperconsultancy.nl/Red-OpenGL/timeline)Tools dir includes some useful libs such as C-Library.reds  to use with Red Samples dir has to be completed but yet includes some samples adapted from orignal codes in C